cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper proposes algorithms to improve the monotonicity of supervised learning models, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The evaluation of the proposed algorithms is conducted on image classification tasks (MNIST), which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the consistency and probability of the algorithms, which are concepts related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and neural networks (cs.NE).
